---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="AI Developer focused on automation, local-first apps, and AI.">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-[65ch] px-6 py-20">
    <div class="border border-terracotta/30 rounded-lg p-8 md:p-12">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-6">
        <img
          src="/images/tarlow-cropped-headshot-small.jpg"
          alt="Tarlow"
          class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover border-2 border-terracotta/20"
          onerror="this.style.display='none'"
        />
      </div>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">About Tarlow</h1>
      <div class="mt-4 h-0.5 w-12 rounded bg-terracotta"></div>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-[1.0625rem] leading-relaxed text-ink/80">
        <p>Hello, I'm Tarlow.</p>
          <p>
            Ever since I was a kid, I’ve been driven by a simple curiosity: the desire to build. Taking a spark of an idea and turning it into a functional, tangible tool has always been my favorite challenge. Over the years, that passion for tinkering has evolved into my primary focus, and that is to help others bring their most ambitious ideas to life.
          </p>
          <p>
            With over 20 years of combined experience across internet marketing, web development, automation, and AI. I specialize in bridging the gap between real-world business needs and technical execution. I love solving the disconnect where clunky technology slows down processes and causes friction.
          </p>
          <p>
            My focus is on designing clean, intuitive systems and automated applications that actually serve a purpose. If your project requires structure, optimization, or automation, I can help you make it happen.
          </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 border border-terracotta/30 rounded-lg p-8 md:p-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Let's Connect</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-[1.0625rem] text-ink/70">
        Interested in working together or just want to chat about automation and AI?
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="mailto:tarlowspace@proton.me"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-terracotta text-paper font-serif text-lg no-underline hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
        >
          Send me an Email
        </a>
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg border border-terracotta/30 text-ink/40 font-serif text-lg cursor-default"
        >
          Discord (coming soon)
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
